{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so in fact, I noticed on couple of other guys, that when they were asking-- these were all wretched souls by now, OK?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were all so long in prison, and wretched and sick souls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they would start off begging a little bit, like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh doctor, please help me, I don't want to die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And naturally I don't, by any means, mean to mean fun of it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't get me wrong at all here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were wretched souls that felt-- that hoped that this guy has a little bit of humanity in him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I noticed, whenever they would whine like that, this guy got mad, this doctor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would just hit them in the face or in the belly, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these-- these helpers would hold the guy by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I noticed-- for-- there were two things that were in my favor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Number one, I was the last in-- in line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And number two, I really had my brain working very, very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I noticed that this guy doesn't like the whining.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so I figured when my turn comes, I better speak up, like in the military, German military-like fashion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it came to that, when I-- when-- when I-- I came forward to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "These guys were holding me right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- and he says, well, what's the matter with you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like he'd ask anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And these other guys would start whining, some of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, well, Herr General, please look at this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a very snappy form, I said that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not snappy, like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This wasn't snappy, the way I said it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time a very snappy form.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he looks at me like he sees a miracle.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
